Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:02.06,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:03.25,B2,MASAYHOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.19,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get rid of the Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.92,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.30,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.57,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:05.63,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going for a little workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:07.89,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Go find somewhere to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:11.55,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:43.29,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I felt an awfully \Nfamiliar Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.28,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Was it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:57.24,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Father... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.75,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.63,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:29.89,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.00,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.67,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Mr. Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.36,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,That Hollow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.48,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,was the one who killed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.54,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone can rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.96,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:48.67,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.62,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,If I had come here sooner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.71,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I may have been able to \Nprotect your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.00,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.92,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for you to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.78,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.49,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.15,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Um... My name is Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.53,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, \Nplease tell me yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.44,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Masayoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.23,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's written with the \Ncharacters for "justice."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.26,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Masayoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.45,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.39,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:29.00,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It is you, Yachiru! \NIt's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.50,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.79,B2,MASAYHOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:41.09,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is this enough wood for the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.75,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:47.95,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That'll last us until \Nmorning. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.87,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Want some konpeito sugar candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.73,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.41,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.40,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.73,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Have some, Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.40,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.04,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:10.26,B2,MASAYOSHI (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:13.22,B2,MASAYOSHI (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,You're not only the \Nlieutenant of Squad 11,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:15.10,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,you're chairwoman \Nof the Women's Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.65,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Reaper Association as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.96,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,You're really working \Nhard. That's terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.11,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you might say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:23.34,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,What've you been doing, Mappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.64,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been traveling as part of a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.86,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Partisan Squad that goes \Nafter drifting Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.75,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,That's hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.37,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.31,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's like going on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.99,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect job for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.01,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun staying \Nat home, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.46,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.10,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I had a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.57,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Had?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:50.62,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow...killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:58.16,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That day, we got into \Na fight over nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:01.77,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and I left on a mission \Nwithout making up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.79,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Several weeks later,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:08.47,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,when I finally got back after \Nfinishing my assignment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:22.22,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have at least \Ntold her, "I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.99,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted her forgiveness. A \Nsimple "that's okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.22,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I despise Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.35,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get rid of \Nevery single damn Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:36.64,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,And some day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:40.76,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to cut down the \NHollow that killed my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:45.24,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see to it that not a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:47.24,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,single person has to suffer \Nlike Mayu and I did
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.20,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,because of Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.36,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill every last one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.26,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That's the promise I \Nmade to my late wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.60,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I sort of got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.45,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I'm rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:06.12,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep going until you \Ndefeat every last Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.47,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.36,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.24,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Masayoshi is amazing, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.75,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,He is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.46,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.02,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... If you go straight from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.64,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,you'll come to the forest you \Nwere talking about, Yachiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.27,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,But it's awfully far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:38.35,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. I run very fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.94,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for showing me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.11,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Um...Ma...Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:46.44,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.23,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-Mayu! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.16,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.31,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayu-Mayu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.67,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.83,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,You've cut down so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.48,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.15,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.05,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Remember Mappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.80,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:19.64,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Masayoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.45,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I ran into him for \Nthe first time in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.01,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,He looked good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.87,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,You met him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:29.26,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.03,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.20,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.48,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,We became friends right after
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.73,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,we both joined the Thirteen \NCourt Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.82,B2,YACHIRU (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mappy, want some konpeito sugar candy? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.52,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks, Yachiru. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.02,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't get enough sweets. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.48,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}These are great! Can I have some more? {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.72,B2,YACHIRU (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.13,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:38.72,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.39,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to come, Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.63,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.29,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.50,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.43,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.65,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:14.71,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.60,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.79,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.34,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:20.78,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.73,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.51,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.71,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I want one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:38.07,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.18,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:46.54,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I remember your wife was \Na great cook too, Mappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:51.04,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... She was, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.06,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what did you argue \Nwith your wife about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.02,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Something silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.72,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.97,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It was because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.01,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:13.60,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That day... That day, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.80,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.44,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I sense a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:20.09,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.49,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't sense anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.37,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru, look after Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.41,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.29,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,going to get rid of the Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.87,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.60,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.71,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:52.70,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Masayoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.93,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru, Mayu, you're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.14,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:04.53,B2,HOLLOW B,0000,0000,0000,,I found you, despicable Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.74,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Masayoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:29.13,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,When you finish your work here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.58,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be going somewhere \Nelse, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.05,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.24,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing Hollows and \Ngetting rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.61,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:42.91,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,I...don't have a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.07,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I went with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.50,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.90,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting dark, so \Nwe should go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.10,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.44,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.18,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.89,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Yachiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:14.60,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get too close to Mappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:15.99,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.70,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,This is far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.09,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.48,B2,MAYU (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Masayoshi... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.55,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.43,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.44,B2,HOLLOW B,0000,0000,0000,,You've come at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:01.18,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Masayoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:03.82,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Let Mayu go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:06.90,B2,HOLLOW B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll let her go, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.52,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:11.45,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.54,B2,HOLLOW B,0000,0000,0000,,We have no more use for that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.48,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about, Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.10,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.36,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,So that no one has to be sad anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:36.60,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Masayoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:40.56,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu... Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.06,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.49,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu, I promise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.78,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill every Hollow \Nuntil none remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.45,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.42,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.54,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... I'd better \Nget rid of them quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.17,B2,HOLLOW B,0000,0000,0000,,A Zanpakuto... What a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.84,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.34,B2,HOLLOW B,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.51,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.94,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:18.81,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.82,B2,HOLLOW B,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.75,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Masayoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:55.76,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.41,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:03.35,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to get close to Mappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.28,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Yachiru... You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.16,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have trouble finding \Nour Spiritual Pressures?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.06,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.78,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Though, the one I wanted revenge against
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.74,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:22.81,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:29.48,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.01,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I got rid of all the Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.73,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's still one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.64,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.01,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Right in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.01,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.36,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.61,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Yachiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:47.09,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.05,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.39,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mappy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.19,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,you're a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.74,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:58.77,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,How am I a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.43,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy used to love sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.84,B2,YACHIRU (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mappy, want some konpeito sugar candy? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.55,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks, Yachiru. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:14.01,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't get enough sweets. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:23.48,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,You still have a heart, Mappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:24.94,B2,MASAYHOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're looking well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.05,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, I sort of got carried away. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:30.78,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:31.97,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.32,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,One day, even that will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:40.64,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,One day, you'll completely \Nbecome a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.34,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.13,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.32,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Not a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.24,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.94,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,What was your wife's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:49.33,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:51.88,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:53.25,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.97,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.96,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why can't I remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.22,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.24,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.28,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get my revenge on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.81,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,the Hollow that killed my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.48,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed your \Nwife is you, Mappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:16.47,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What...happened? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.45,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You Hollow... You bastard! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.99,B2,MASAYOSHI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You killed her! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:29.46,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I...I'm the one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.94,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:37.60,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,While you were chasing after \Na Hollow, it possessed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:44.69,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,When you saw yourself in the \Nmirror after killing your wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.29,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,your consciousness took over the Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:53.11,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,But... Just like you forgot \Nyour love for candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:56.22,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,and even your wife's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.43,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,One day, your consciousness \Nwill also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:03.24,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...I...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.88,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.43,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayu..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.11,B2,HOLLOW B,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die...alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.49,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Masayoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.39,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Masayoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.57,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.26,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu... I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.61,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:09.30,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I promised you I'd kill every \NHollow until none remain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.79,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.59,B2,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:23.28,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.00,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.75,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this? It was your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:38.30,B2,MASAYOSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's sweet...and good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.55,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Mappy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.99,B2,MASAYOSHI (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep on fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:07.24,B2,MASAYOSHI (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,so no one has to be sad anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.37,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.00,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:24.64,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.98,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,You can have them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.55,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny, you're so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:44.82,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:45.94,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:22.95,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So the next one's going to be our \Nlast stand-alone episode, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:24.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's natural for \Nme to wrap up the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:27.38,B2,TOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, I'm going to be staying in \Nthe World of the Living for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:28.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.62,B2,TOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Will I cause you some inconvenience?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:30.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.46,B2,TOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Be seeing you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:34.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,My chance for action.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:36.56,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:44.69,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:46.69,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I caught this many!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.65,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Nice. So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.04,0:23:50.15,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:55.13,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's been several \Ndays, but we still haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:57.37,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,reached the Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.87,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,We're lost, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:03.82,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.